flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Receipt of supplier acknowledgment via EDI or portal.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Receive supplier acknowledgment]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Detect discrepancies]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Remote Functions - Resolve discrepancies}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Update PO terms]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Maintain PO integration]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Escalate unacknowledged POs]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced cycle time, improved COGS, timely PO closure, and strengthened working capital through efficient acknowledgment and issue resolution.]
  N3 -->|High discrepancy cost| B1[Escalate to human review]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention for high-cost discrepancies]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Supplier reliability low| B2[Escalate to negotiation team]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Negotiate terms with unreliable suppliers]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Integration failure| B3[Trigger rollback and retry]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Ensure reliable PO data exchange]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]